# Normalize line endings: store text as LF in the repo and check it out as LF
# on every platform, so Windows autocrlf can't reintroduce CRLF and trip
# Prettier's `endOfLine: "lf"` / `nx format:check`.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary files must never be treated as text or line-ending-converted.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.eot binary
